spec: agent-core.ai-docs/v1
namespace: "Infrastructure\\Storage"
fqcn: "Ineersa\\AgentCore\\Infrastructure\\Storage"
description: "Storage adapters — in-memory stores, Flysystem run logs, Doctrine event store, hot prompt state, local artifact store."
files[9]{file,type,responsibility,docs}:
  InMemoryRunStore.php,class,In-memory RunStoreInterface — map-based get/compareAndSwap/findRunningStaleBefore for testing and stale-run recovery.,docs/InMemoryRunStore.md
  InMemoryCommandStore.php,class,In-memory CommandStoreInterface — enqueue/has/countPending/pending/rejectPendingByKind/markApplied/markRejected/markSuperseded for testing.,docs/InMemoryCommandStore.md
  InMemoryOutboxStore.php,class,In-memory OutboxStoreInterface — enqueue/claim/markProcessed/markFailed for testing.,docs/InMemoryOutboxStore.md
  InMemoryPromptStateStore.php,class,In-memory PromptStateStoreInterface — get/save/delete for testing.,docs/InMemoryPromptStateStore.md
  RunEventStore.php,class,Doctrine-backed EventStoreInterface — appends/retrieves RunEvents using Doctrine DBAL/ORM.,docs/RunEventStore.md
  HotPromptStateStore.php,class,Doctrine-backed PromptStateStoreInterface — persists hot prompt state snapshots for fast replay avoidance.,docs/HotPromptStateStore.md
  LocalArtifactStore.php,class,Local filesystem ArtifactStoreInterface — stores artifacts under a base directory using Flysystem.,docs/LocalArtifactStore.md
  RunLogWriter.php,class,Writes RunEvents as JSONL lines to Flysystem storage — append-only run log for audit and replay fallback.,docs/RunLogWriter.md
  RunLogReader.php,class,Reads JSONL run logs from Flysystem storage — parses lines back into RunEvent objects for replay.,docs/RunLogReader.md
